headline: Jacobs Expanding Services to Strengthen and Modernize Alaska's Vital Maritime Infrastructure Hub
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has received a five-year contract extension to continue serving as Program Management Consultant for the Don Young Port of Alaska (Port of Alaska) Modernization Program, a phased multi-billion-dollar program to replace all the Port's aging waterfront infrastructure with modern, resilient facilities.
